message.body: What time do you need a babysitter?
Arg, the flynn won't tell me whether they are cancelling or not, so I should prep either way. Lemme ask her dad and get back to you in 5. I would pay you, of course, have you babysat before?
You and z are old buds ;)
Ive only babysat a couple times, but ive been working with kids for a few years
Oh yeah! Ok, well how about 1 to 3? 20 bucks? Snow fun?
I could also do noon to 3, but I think 1 to 3 is crucial
Sounds good, ill see yal at 1
I'm so annoyed, the Flynn won't cancel but I feel like folks arent gonna come out in this. We just came in from outside, so I think z will wanna play games a d read Inside, is ok?
